<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/Services-Page.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/comp.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/Components.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../images/logo.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>Our Services</title>
</head>
<body >
    <% if (UserData.loggedin) { %>
        <%- include('./partials/nav2')%></body>
    <% } else { %>
        <%- include('./partials/navbar')%></body>
    <% } %>
    
    <div id="dav">

    </div>
    <div class="l1" id="scrolldown">
        <svg class="arrow-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" viewBox="9 -20 32 72">
          <path d="M 20 5 Q 22 0 25 0 T 30 5 L 45 30 Q 45 35 40 35 T 10 35 Q 5 35 5 30 Z"  />
        </svg>      
      </div>  
     <section class="serviceslist">
        <a href="#div-1">EHR Management</a>
        <a href="#div-2">Prescription Management</a>
        <a href="#div-3">Appointment Scheduling</a>
        <a href="#div-4">Direct Consultation</a>
        <a href="#div-5">Telemedicine Communication</a>
        <a href="#div-6">Emergency Medical Information</a>
        <a href="#div-7">Patient Education Resources</a>
        <a href="#div-8">Support Community</a>
        <a href="#div-9">Medicine Management </a>
    </section>
    <section class="section2">
        <div id="div-1" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>EHR Management</h1>
                <p>When it comes to maintaining a record of all our patients to date, our health record system succeeds in maintaining all known details of patient's illnesses, to ensure that should a complication or mutation of such an illness appear in the future, we will have ample data to combat it.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="../images/ehr.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-2" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Prescription Management</h1>
                <p>We provide faultless remedies and solutions designed to cure all known ailments. Made using natural and healthy materials, we aim to provide medicine that can be trusted by our clients, and that remains unparalleled in purity and efficacy.</p>    
            </div>
            <img src="../images/pres.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-3" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Appointment Scheduling</h1>
                <p>With our capable doctors and pharmacists being available all day round, there is never a shortage of practitioners available for appointments. Featuring on call appointments, Whatsapp appointments and email appointment bookings, alongside a team of doctors for all known illnesses, there is never a shortage of doctors for appointments.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="../images/app.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-4" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Direct Consultation</h1>
                <p>Patients possess the right to visit our doctors and to discuss treatment plans and prescription dosages. A full diagnosis is provided to the patient at the end of the consultation to ensure the client is well informed about their current condition and of any complications.</p>    
            </div>
            <img src="../images/dire.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-5" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Telemedicine Communication</h1>
                <p>Our on call doctors are always available for patients that opt for consultations over the telephone. Our telecommunication features a flawless connection, with no lags to voice or any delay to sound, further ensuring a pristine communication that is indiscernible from direct consultations.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="../images/tele.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-6" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Emergency Medical Information</h1>
                <p>Should an illness develop a complication that is deemed as an emergency, patients will be elated to know that in such critical situations, patients will receive maximum care from our doctors, ensuring their complete recovery, even in severe emergencies.</p>    
            </div>
            <img src="../images/emer.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-7" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Patient Education Resources</h1>
                <p>An illness, no matter how common, is always capable of demanding more knowledge from doctors. It is our staff members duty to embark on this journey of acquiring knowledge alongside their patient, in order to deepen not only their own understanding of the disease, but to also aid their patient in increasing their understanding of their condition.
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src="../images/pat.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-8" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Support Community</h1>
                <p>
                    It matters not who our patient is, or where they come from. In our care, all patients are treated and acknowledged equally. Our facilities feature staff from all backgrounds of life, so our patients will always find a staff member from the same roots as them, further ensuring ethical behaviour, and preserving a supportive community.
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src="../images/sup.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div id="div-9" class="outer">
            <div class="inner">
                <h1>Medicine Management</h1>
                <p>
                    Our storage of medicine is more than enough to treat generations of patients over. Handled by pharmacists to ensure that our patients recieve the perfect amount of medicine for their diseases, to ensure patient health alongside medicine amount longevity.
                </p>
            </div>
            <img src="../images/med.jpeg" alt="" height="300px" width="600px">
        </div>
    </section>
  
    <%- include('./partials/Footer')%></body>


 <script>
 
 // Event listener for services scrolling
 const serviceLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.serviceslist a');
 
 serviceLinks.forEach(link => {
     link.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
         event.preventDefault();
         
         const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);
         
         const targetSection = document.getElementById(targetId);
         
         targetSection.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
        });
    });
    
    // Event listener for services scrolling
    const scrolls = document.querySelector('.l1');
    console.log('sad');
    
    scrolls.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
        const targetSection = document.getElementById('dav');
        console.log(targetSection);
        
            targetSection.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
        });        
 </script>
</body>
</html>